0.replace the file in etc/hadoop/(hadoop installed path) and conf/(spark installed path) with the configure files in this folder.

#do follow steps when add the new node to cluster
1.configure /etc/hosts, and add new node of cluster

2.configure etc/hadoop/slaves in the hadoop installed path, and add new node of cluster.

3.configure conf/slaves in the spark installed path, and add new node of cluster.
